high_descs: Turn around to your right then walk straight turn to your left facing the fridge
Open the fridge pick up the glass inside then close the fridge
Turn to your left the walk straight to the sink counter
Put the glass on the left side of the apple on the counter
Pick up the knife in front of the paper bag
Put the knife in the glass
anns.task_desc: Put the knife in the cold glass

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the fridge on your left
Open the fridge and pick up the orange chalice that is sitting on the top shelf then close the fridge
Turn left and cross the room the the counter to the right of the sink
Place the chalice on the counter to the left of the apple
Pick up the knife that is behind the chalice and apple
Place the knife in the chalice
anns.task_desc: Place a knife in a chalice

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator and take out the orange cup, then close the refrigerator.
Turn left and walk forward to the counter.
Put the cup on the counter, to the left of the apple.
Pick up the knife behind the apple on the counter.
Put the knife in the cup.
anns.task_desc: Place a cup with a knife in it on a counter top.
